1. Install the HubsPot cli

```
npm install @hubspot/cli
```

2. Install the boiler plate 

```
hs create website-theme my-website-theme
```

Optional: Push the new files to Github (check the Github Documentation)
Optional: Install Tailwind (check the Tailwind Documentation)

3. Authenticate and upload the Hubspot Files. 

Add the script in package.json
 "hsupload": "hs upload \"_hb_official\" \"_hb_official\" "


```
hs init
npm run hsupload
```


